sectionText: Course & associated labs restricted to the following majors: Agricultural Engineering, General Engineering, and Industrial Engineering. This section covers parametric solid modeling and is recommended for ISE and ABE students.
sectionNotes: Restricted to Agr Engineering & Agr Science or Agricultural Engineering or Engineering Mechanics or General Engineering or Industrial Engineering or Industrial Design or Agricultural & Biological Engr or Engineering Undeclared or Systems Engineering and Design major(s).
